        "### 🧪 Upgraded PGM & Gibbs Sampling Engine (THRML Native)\n",
        "\n",
        "In this version, we define the inference as a **Probabilistic Graphical Model**. The transformer hidden state acts as an external field acting on a `CategoricalNode` (the token), and the `GibbsBlock` performs the state transitions based on the energy landscape."
